Shanghai foreign investment 57 pct in industry . Of total foreign - invested projects in Shanghai in the first half , 57 . 1 percent flowed into industrial projects , the China Business Times said on Monday . Foreign - funded projects in the real estate and public utilities accounted for 17 . 45 percent of the total , it said . The newspaper did not give total projects or the contracted amount for the period , but said 95 foreign - funded projects involved investment of more than $ 10 million each . - - Beijing Newsroom ( 8610 ) 6532 1921 
